radio_data.name: Flash FM
radio_data.notes: internal_name is the filename ajaxamp should use, id is the track ID as seen in the game's memory, loop_track is used to tell ajaxamp if a specific track should loop or not, start_from_beginning is used to tell if a track should start from beginning or if it should start on a position specified by the game, audio_file_type is the type of audio that should be used, 0 is music, 1 is sfx, 2 is cutscenes, override_by_ajaxamp is used to tell if a track should be played through the game itself or if it should be played through ajaxamp, custom_volume_level is a custom volume level that should be used by ajaxamp
